title: This is just too easy! Res Lease in Austin. 4 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: ['Location, location, location!', 'Only 6.5 miles to downtown', '.', 'This beautiful 2-story home has 4 bedrooms, and 2 and a half bathrooms.', 'It has a delightful covered deck and pergola that spans the entire length of the home on the back and abundant natural light brightening the home.', 'There is also a gas line to the patio for a BBQ grill.', 'The downstairs of this home has tile flooring and the kitchen has quartz countertops!', 'There are delightful, modern finishes throughout the property.', 'Upstairs there is carpet throughout the central hallway and the bedrooms.', 'The upstairs bathrooms are well updated as well, and the laundry closet is conveniently located upstairs.', 'The HOA takes care of lawn services front and back, watering the yard, and garbage.', 'Google Fiber is available as well!', "Come and tour this home before it's gone!", '--to set up a viewing--', 'Call/Text/Email ANYTIME!', 'Cristian Argueta', 'show contact info', '(ask for ID# 8414234)', 'All City Real Estate Company', 'Have other properties available....', '(Houses, Duplexes, Apartments, Condos, All Areas)', 'Please be Aware of SCAMS...', 'Do NOT reply to this ad, please call/text for a fast response.', 'Listed By: Orlando Solis, Fuse Realty, LLC']
